[00:01.21] We knew the world would not be the same
[00:05.85] A few people laughed, a few people cried, most people were silent
[00:14.94] I remembered the line from the Hindu scripture, the Bhagavad-gītā
[00:21.88] Vishnu is trying to persuade the Prince that he should do his duty
[00:29.65] And to impress him, takes on his multi-armed form
[00:35.89] And says, "Now I am become Death, the destroyer of worlds"
[00:44.33] I suppose we all thought that, one way or another